<para id="fs-id34053590">The sub-VI for the rather trivial operation of converting a 

string of bits to bit-words is shown above in Figure 1. Only basic knowledge of 

LabVIEW is required to implement this module. While some may argue it's trivial and 

non-deserving of its own sub-VI, modularity and readability still prevail in good 

design technique, and this transmitter is no exception.</para>


<para id="fs-id33938971">
<figure id="layout">
