  <caption>This is the LabVIEW block diagram for the Bits-to-Words sub-VI.</caption>
</figure>


</para><para id="fs-id18908739">Figure 2 above shows the block diagram layout. The 

parallel bits are taken as an input and fed into the built-in LabVIEW function 

"Reshape Array," which groups the number of bits appropriately.</para>



